64/apple-watch-series-10-review-smartwatch-wearables&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10&lt;/a>; 旁边有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/19/24248380/apple-watch-ultra-2-black-smartwatch-wearables&quot;>;黑色演绎&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/23878981/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-review-double-tap- precision-finding-siri&quot;>;Apple Watch Ultra 2.&lt;/a>;。每款可穿戴设备都有自己的优点和缺点，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23369207/apple-watch-se-2022-review-smartwatch&quot;>;第二代 Apple Watch SE&lt;/ a>;，但最近推出的新型可穿戴设备也意味着现在市场上的 Apple Watch 型号比以往任何时候都多，而且还有更多优惠。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;CWUc7k&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;sHcaqK&quot;>;但是面对所有这些选项，您应该选择哪一个？一般来说，您希望购买您能买得起的最新款手表，以便它能够继续接收来自 Apple 的软件更新。最新更新 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/25/24253366/watch-os-11-apple-watch-smartwatch&quot;>;watchOS 11&lt;/a>; 于 9 月推出在 Apple Watch Series 6 及更新版本上，最终将那些仍在使用旧款 Series 4 或 Series 5 的人抛在了后面。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;C0aQBE&quot;>;P...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals</id><author><name>布兰登·威德</name></author></entry></feed>